\addvspace {10\p@ }
\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {17.1}{\ignorespaces P95 violation severity versus dropout rate. The DC3S shield (blue) achieves zero severity across all dropout rates, confirming Theorem~\ref {thm:safety-preservation}.}}{92}{figure.caption.51}%
