\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {20.1}{\ignorespaces Coverage--width tradeoff under temporal extension. As the certificate ages (horizontal axis), the coverage probability decreases while the interval width increases. The half-life (vertical dashed line) marks the crossover point.}}{107}{figure.caption.58}%
