\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {21.1}{\ignorespaces ORIUS universal 5-stage pipeline. Each domain plugs in a \texttt {DomainAdapter}; the DC3S core (stages 1--5) is shared and domain-agnostic.}}{113}{figure.caption.60}%
\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {21.2}{\ignorespaces Canonical universal ORIUS validation surface. Battery is shown as the locked reference aggregate; industrial and healthcare are the current proof-validated non-battery rows; AV remains a proof candidate; navigation is synthetic-shadow evidence; and aerospace remains experimental.}}{115}{figure.caption.64}%
\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {21.3}{\ignorespaces Cross-domain validation surface from the canonical universal evidence tier table. The labels encode the defended claim boundary: reference, proof-validated, proof-candidate, shadow-synthetic, and experimental.}}{116}{figure.caption.66}%
